To local view sum, giving i32.
Let cells be buffer of 6 i32 filled with 0.
For each index i of cells: cells at i becomes i plus 1.
Let middle be view of cells from 2 for 3.
Let total be 0.
For each index i of middle: total becomes total plus middle at i.
Give total.

To main, giving i32.
Give local view sum.
